Package: rnrfa
Type: Package
Title: UK National River Flow Archive data from R
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2014-04-26
Author: Claudia Vitolo <claudia.vitolo@gmail.com>, Matthew Fry <mfry@ceh.ac.uk>
Maintainer: Claudia Vitolo <claudia.vitolo@gmail.com>
Description: Utility functions to retrieve data from the UK National River Flow Archive. The package contains R wrappers to the UK NRFA data APIs (http://www.ceh.ac.uk/data/nrfa/). There are functions to retrieve stations falling in a bounding box, to generate a map and extracting time series and general information. It also contain the dataset \code{StationSummary}.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.2)
Imports: XML2R, RCurl, stringr, zoo, rjson, rgdal, sp, rCharts
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyLoad: yes
URL: http://www.ceh.ac.uk/data/nrfa/
stringsAsFactors: FALSE
NeedsCompilation: no
